<section id="block-block-12" class="block block-block main-section section-white welcome-text clearfix">

        <h2 class="block-title">Welcome to the Centre for Free Expression</h2>
    
  <p>The Centre for Free Expression at Ryerson University is a hub for public education, research and advocacy on free expression and the public’s right to know. Our work is undertaken in collaboration with academic and community-based organizations across Canada and internationally.</p>

</section>
